longBusinessSummary: Hua Lien International (Holding) Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the cultivation of sugar cane, and manufacturing of sugar businesses. It operates through Supporting Services, Sugar Business, and Ethanol Business segments. The company is also involved in the provision of supporting services to customers in the sweetener and ethanol business; and ethanol biofuel business. It operates in Jamaica and the United States. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Central, Hong Kong.
